{"tid":1362035,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"海員有野同大家講","createTime":"2019-07-24T17:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T11:50:08.000Z","uid":14982,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e21d973a1c50320d365fb318db26b03a35beed1b","tid":1362035,"uid":14982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:56:52.000Z","msg":"生係香港 心繫香港<br />\n<br />\n我係嚟自航運界行船嘅香港人，喺逃犯條例修訂出現後，雖然我一直喺大海漂泊，但仍然一直關注香港所發生嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n有時喺海到唔係好上到網，好多時幾日先上到一次網，資訊好少，都係靠朋友WhatsApp講俾我知發生咩事。睇到啲人衝入鐵站打人、打大肚婆，我係呆咗，我估唔到香港會變到咁。每次見到啲新聞個心真係好唔舒服。<br />\n<br />\n我愛香港，係香港有言論自由、有制度，畀到安全感我。啲中國船員連國際最低工資水平都未達到，係船上面工作更加感受到中國人做嘢亂咁嚟，完全唔跟守則，唔注意安全。<br />\n<br />\n我愛香港，香港有新聞自由，唔似啲中國人永遠沉醉係自己世界。<br />\n<br />\n我係香港個時成日嫌三嫌四，但我知道香港的確係一個好好嘅地方，一個我好鍾意嘅地方。同中國人一齊工作更加切身體會到我地嘅唔同。我地有我地嘅體制，我地生活得好好，唔需要被同化，唔需要被中國人改變。<br />\n<br />\n但香港警方今時今日使用過度武力既行為同內地城管有咩分別？<br />\n官商鄉黑警相互勾結，香港竟然倒退成咁，慢慢俾中國侵蝕。<br />\n<br />\n人不在，心在。<br />\n遺憾唔可以同大家一齊守護香港呢個咁美好既家園，最自由既香港。我好希望呢朵花，能夠伴著我，隨著大海，散播到世界各地。<br />\n<br />\n香港人 香港心 香港就是我家<br />\n<br />\n(代朋友post)<br />\n<br />\n我地係香港人，我愛我地嘅屋企。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvRdXTi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvRdXTi.png&h=f1ddefa7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da959fd8359417de3d22968f2366dabae3bfea38","tid":1362035,"uid":278765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:06:14.000Z","msg":"讚！👍<br />\n推"},{"pid":"2c963bb44335ab622841a6c385b8bbd285401e4d","tid":1362035,"uid":288965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37277a2cc3ab4598ef3e4f1dec2bd7ede57479e0","tid":1362035,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:07:39.000Z","msg":"遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ccfb337beb6884fab2e067d4d025cae794f473","tid":1362035,"uid":276558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c4f8d4013331a5006b0cb2acbd54887bf31a7e","tid":1362035,"uid":236847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:58:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd7142a126e8fc65827c103fcebbc0785d3d014","tid":1362035,"uid":80249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:22:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02569258b32dffe4a5c0e2ad533cd51031502e3c","tid":1362035,"uid":215611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:28:36.000Z","msg":"紅簿又好<br />\n本地船長牌又好<br />\n遊艇牌都好<br />\n總之乜柒都貼上黎支持啦"},{"pid":"95783af5d1d34d8d88b70c96406cb9527118064d","tid":1362035,"uid":284732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb81a8430b69dd0a05ba12ae54948a1b21b0be2","tid":1362035,"uid":14982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212671b4ca03cc21a3d2029e76141e9540233fc3","tid":1362035,"uid":291336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:26:52.000Z","msg":"放心 仲有我地一直係度<br />\n<a href=\"http